stated in individual files included in this package.


components:
Makefile        general make file for code
Makeconf        configuration for the make setup.  This file includes
                optimization flags for various compilers.
src             source code
examples        Examples and test code for each element in the library.
licenses        Copies of the licenses used for the pieces of this package.

derived components (after make):
docs            produced by 'make doc' and contains api documentation.
lib             produced by 'make' and contains libraries of the package.
include         produced by 'make' and contains header files for the package.

